{"tid":347613,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"田少抽擊消失的波兒　「乜咁快換咗財爺」","createTime":"2017-08-05T03:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T04:32:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85421e6eeb1dcc27d8689b360e5966e9f1393df6","tid":347613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:36:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20112354&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20112354%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170805&d=Ojd2XZwUuNL6cbgivLjUcZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=85120cfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20112354%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170805&h=70296249\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20112354&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170805</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n田少抽擊消失的波兒　<br />\n「乜咁快換咗財爺」 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、金管局前總裁任志剛前日重出江湖再喺網誌《觀點》撰文發功，除咗力撐特首林鄭月娥嘅「理財新哲學」，為林鄭用萬億財政儲備開路之外，仲順手不點名插埋上手財爺、薯片叔叔曾俊華係「守財奴」。以任總江湖地位，自然引來政、商界議論紛紛，不過最到肉嘅「評論」仲係自由黨榮譽主席田北俊，佢一句「乜咁快已經換咗財爺喇？」完全說出了重點來。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n田少噚日出po寸任總同消失的波兒，引起網民熱議。田北俊fb截圖<br />\n<br />\nfb分享任總新聞<br />\n<br />\n田少噚日係fb分享任總段新聞，之後話：「我只不過離開咗香港兩日啫，乜咁快已經換咗財爺喇？」仲hashtag咗#被遺忘的波兒、#行會成員做埋財政司嗰份、#薯片躺着也中槍。其實明眼人都睇到，任總連《基本法》第107條都解釋埋，話冇話唔可以用赤字預算，根本係財爺做嘅野，咁樣叫陳茂波情何以堪呢？田少個po引嚟近兩百網民留言、逾2,500人回應，有人好認同田少講法，話又唔見任總早幾年出聲？但亦有人支持任總，話搞全民退休保障、起老人院有乜唔好呀？&nbsp;<br />\n有財經界中人話，其實將財政儲備還富於民冇人會反對，問題係點用啫！經歷過梁振英年代，市民係擔心林鄭又將錢用埋喺討好大陸嘅基建工程、又或者明益建制，更甚就係為民望大派福利，將納稅人辛辛苦苦儲落嘅錢亂花，如果政府有心還富於民，其實最好就減稅，特別係高樓價之下，好多交足稅又冇乜福利，仲要供樓嘅中產，真係好辛苦㗎！<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n￼"},{"pid":"7fcc9e4058181156f2cc00a19c330b2a92147c0a","tid":347613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170805/large/a1202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170805%2Flarge%2Fa1202a.gif&h=f64ddfa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc64193d612d245fe313d41775d344bf31bcd5dd","tid":347613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170805/large/a1202b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170805%2Flarge%2Fa1202b.gif&h=78c2d843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田少噚日出po寸任總同消失的波兒，引起網民熱議。田北俊fb截圖"},{"pid":"95973441b5d20170a1781b5d7e012f749ea4b937","tid":347613,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170805/large/a1202c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170805%2Flarge%2Fa1202c.gif&h=b468d8dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa51e00dafe6549c62e9d35986f068d67d6dd1b1","tid":347613,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d8dfcaaf2f65dc913dc323dc0a223bb5a84bbb","tid":347613,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員係特首幕僚，按慣例可以出將入相，做欽差大人指導除特首以外所有官員。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}